{"tid":2215064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾助潘曉穎家屬開記招倡修例 周浩鼎割蓆：最近冇接觸過潘生潘太","createTime":"2020-09-23T17:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T11:04:51.000Z","uid":182827,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2caa679454b8e22c688c0d8a1157fb9fe039644f","tid":2215064,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077623?fbclid=IwAR3Ssob19Zp_HaXR57bIWjOd8ft9_c1cZQx_2nbgMoDlM9laC6siID3S6Kg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077623%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ssob19Zp_HaXR57bIWjOd8ft9_c1cZQx_2nbgMoDlM9laC6siID3S6Kg&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=c62d1042\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077623%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ssob19Zp_HaXR57bIWjOd8ft9_c1cZQx_2nbgMoDlM9laC6siID3S6Kg&h=631bcabf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077623?fbclid=IwAR3Ssob19Zp_HaXR57bIWjOd8ft9_c1cZQx_2nbgMoDlM9laC6siID3S6Kg</a><br />\n<br />\n事隔一年，周浩鼎被問及對潘母的公開信有何看法。<span class=\"red\">他表示自己「最近冇接觸過潘生潘太」</span>，並指公開信的內容「都係呼籲返陳同佳儘快去自首」，希望政府盡快配合，台灣當局亦可作出應對。<span class=\"red\">另一民建聯議員葛珮帆則與黨友鄭泳舜的回應如出一轍，指自己「未睇」公開信，未能作出回應</span>。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯完美演繹咩叫用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能連潘生潘太個contact都delete左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b51c090f22d278446cb42dd35a813f2eca0088","tid":2215064,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:05:33.000Z","msg":"潘生太 應該出來指證港共同保皇黨假仁假義啦"},{"pid":"c3b5bdb8ed1bc0b2cfff8510fdcedd5b3b63d931","tid":2215064,"uid":37992,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"b0b51c090f22d278446cb42dd35a813f2eca0088","tid":2215064,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:05:33.